sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client App
    participant A as Agent
    participant P as Proxy
    participant T as Target

    A->>P: Auth
    P-->>A: AuthResponse success
    A->>P: ConnectRequest(request_id, target, Tcp/Udp)
    P->>T: TCP/UDP connect
    P-->>A: ConnectResponse success
    C->>A: payload bytes
    A->>P: Data(stream_id=request_id, data)
    P->>T: payload bytes
    T-->>P: response bytes
    P-->>A: Data(stream_id=request_id, data)
    A-->>C: response bytes
    A->>P: Data(stream_id, empty, is_end=true)
